   "stance": "supports",
   "quote": "The 2026 edition shows that commercial colocation and hyperscale facilities now provide more than two-thirds of Europe’s IT power, driven by the growing demand for cloud and AI."
  },
  {
   "url": "https://www.cloudfest.com/blog/frankfurt-overtake-london-colocation-data-center-market-educa-report",
   "stance": "supports",
   "quote": "With over two-thirds of “IT power” delivered by commercial colocation and hyperscale facilities, that’s a substantial reordering of the European compute landscape."
  },
  {
   "url": "https://www.bundeswirtschaftsministerium.de/Redaktion/EN/Publikationen/Digitale-Welt/status-and-development-of-the-german-data-centre-landscape-executive-summary.pdf?__blob=publicationFile&v=2",
   "stance": "supports",
   "quote": "With over 2,000 data centres and an installed IT power demand of over 2,700 MW, Ger many is already the largest centre for digital infra structure in Europe."
  },
  {
